title: Starship SN10 Rolls Out to Boca Chica Launch Site After Starship SN9 Scrubs Launch Attempt
author: NASASpaceflight
description:
SpaceX is set to roll out the Starship SN10 prototype to the Boca Chica launch site after scrubbing today's Starship SN9 launch attempt.
